com.betfair.cougar.core.api

Class GateRegisterer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.core.api.GateRegisterer

  • public class GateRegisterer
extends Object
    A stateless (or even anonymous) bean which registers one or more GateListener instances with a given CougarStartingGate. Use these to save listeners having to register themselves programmatically.

    You can control ordering of listeners in Spring config by having different registerers depend-on each other.
